result.name: 品 PIIN Wine Restaurant

reviews.text:
Absolutely loved the wine and I'm not even a lover of wine! 
The atmosphere as soon as you walk into PIIN is calm and welcoming. There's a great ambience in the room and the staff are very attentive and knowledgeable even able to give me a few great suggestions despite my somewhat limited knowledge. I will soon be back again !!!
Overpriced as usual for restaurants in this area. Not worth the hype.
Interesting match of healthy Cantonese cuisine and fine wines.  Traditional tastes paired with a wide variety of burgundies and other wines.
